title: 1.6.4光影问题求解
author: jianrenshong
txt_content:
#
# A fatal error has been detected by the Java Runtime Environment:
#
#  EXCEPTION_ACCESS_VIOLATION (0xc0000005) at pc=0x000000005eb7934b, pid=10676, tid=1720
#
# JRE version: Java(TM) SE Runtime Environment (7.0_51-b13) (build 1.7.0_51-b13)
# Java VM: Java HotSpot(TM) 64-Bit Server VM (24.51-b03 mixed mode windows-amd64 compressed oops)
# Problematic frame:
# C  [atio6axx.dll+0xd8934b]
#
# Failed to write core dump. Minidumps are not enabled by default on client versions of Windows
#
# If you would like to submit a bug report, please visit:
#   http://bugreport.sun.com/bugreport/crash.jsp

# See problematic frame for where to report the bug.

译文：
##致命错误被检测到的Java运行时环境:## EXCEPTION_ACCESS_VIOLATION(0 xc0000005)在个人电脑= 0 x000000005eb7934b pid = 10676,tid = 1720## JRE版本:Java运行时环境(TM)SE(7.0 _51-b13)(构建1.7.0_51-b13)# Java VM:Java HotSpot(TM)64位服务器虚拟机(24.51 -b03混合模式windows-amd64压缩哦)#有问题的框架:# C[atio6axx.dll + 0 xd8934b]##未能写核心转储。Minidumps不默认启用客户端版本的Windows##如果你想提交错误报告,请访问:# http://bugreport.sun.com/bugreport/crash.jsp#事故发生在本机代码在Java虚拟机。#看到有问题的框架来报告错误的地方。#


这是164版本运行光影的错误，172也有此现象，但171不受影响，一开游戏立即闪退，求解原因
